explanation: [0-0] A long, blue creature is inside a hole in a brown object. There are many holes in the brown object. The blue creature is staring with furrowed brows, its mouth open to reveal its teeth.

[0-10] It slowly opens its mouth wide and sticks out its tongue. There are many holes in its pink tongue. As it opens its mouth, the hole in one of its teeth gets bigger and bigger, then the tooth falls out. It bends down to look at the tooth. Then the camera slowly zooms in. A long, green creature drills out of the tooth hole, spinning around inside. The green creature slowly turns blue, and the tooth gradually turns brown, ultimately returning to the same state as at the beginning.
